# Auth

- POST /auth/register — register a new user
- GET /auth/confirm-email — confirm email
- POST /auth/login — login
- POST /auth/logout — logout
- POST /auth/forgot-password — request password reset
- POST /auth/reset-password — reset password

---

# Users

- GET /users/profile — get current user
- PUT /users/update — update user
- DELETE /users/delete — delete user

---

# Specialists

- POST /specialists/create — create specialist profile
- GET /specialists/me — get my specialist profile
- GET /specialists/get/{specialist_id} — get specialist by id
- PUT /specialists/update — update specialist
- PATCH /specialists/deactivate/{specialist_id} — deactivate specialist (admin)
- PATCH /specialists/activate/{specialist_id} — activate specialist (admin)
- PATCH /specialists/verify/{specialist_id} — verify specialist (admin)
- DELETE /specialists/delete — delete specialist
- GET /specialists/list — list all specialists (admin)
- GET /specialists/search — find nearby specialists

---

# Files (Avatar)

- POST /files/upload/avatar — upload avatar
- GET /files/get/avatar/{user_id} — get avatar (public)
- DELETE /files/delete/avatar/{user_id} — delete avatar

---

# Files (Accreditation)

- POST /files/upload/accreditation — upload accreditation PDF
- GET /files/get/accreditation — get my accreditation
- GET /files/get/accreditation/{specialist_id} — get specialist accreditation
- DELETE /files/delete/accreditation — delete accreditation

---

# Address

- POST /address/add/address — create address
- GET /address/get/address — get my address
- DELETE /address/delete/address — delete address

---

# Catalog

- POST /catalog/add/item — create catalog item
- GET /catalog/get/catalog/{specialist_id} — get specialist catalog
- PUT /catalog/update/{catalog_id} — update catalog item
- DELETE /catalog/delete/{catalog_id} — delete catalog item

---

# Comment

- POST /comment/write/{specialist_id} — write comment
- GET /comment/get/comments/{specialist_id} — get comments
- DELETE /comment/delete/{specialist_id} — delete comment

---

# Rate

- POST /rate/create/{specialist_id} — rate specialist
- GET /rate/get/rate/{specialist_id} — get rates
- DELETE /rate/delete/{specialist_id} — delete rate

---

# Message

- POST /message/write — send message
- GET /message/get/chat/{order_id} — get chat messages

---

# Orders

- POST /orders/create — create order
- GET /orders/get/{order_id} — get order
- GET /orders/my — get my orders (client)
- GET /orders/active — get active orders (specialist)
- GET /orders/specialist/my — get specialist orders
- PUT /orders/update/{order_id} — update order
- POST /orders/take/{order_id} — take order
- POST /orders/complete/{order_id} — complete order
- POST /orders/cancel/{order_id} — cancel order
- DELETE /orders/delete/{order_id} — delete order

---

# Requests

- GET /requests/get/all — get all requests
- PUT /requests/approve/{request_id} — approve request